# apps/api — Backend

- Branch: `feat/api-*`
- Auth: JWT Bearer + global `ApiKeyGuard` (`X-API-Key`); use `@Public()` for health/webhooks/swagger
- Swagger schemes: `bearer` and `X-API-Key` (named)
- Production secrets: see `docs/SECURITY_SECRETS.md`; never copy HomeFix `.env`
- Deploy scripts live under `scripts/deploy/jetbay-be/` — do not touch baotienweb nginx/DB
